Interface IRedisCache<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of values this cache stores.
    U - The type of values this cache returns.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RedisHashCache, RedisListCache, RedisSetCache, RedisSortedSetCache, RedisStringCache

    public interface IRedisCache<T,U>
    Interface for all key-value caches. An IRedisCache caches (key, value, ...) tuples.

      • get

        U get(String key)
        Get the key from the cache. Should return null or equivalent for the Type if the key is not in the cache.
        Parameters:
        key - The key to get
        Returns:
        The value stored at key.

      • removeValue

        Boolean removeValue(String key,
                    T value)
        Remove the value from the cache. Should return false if either the key or the value is not in the cache.
        Parameters:
        key - The key to remove from.
        value - The value to remove in key.
        Returns:
        true if the value was removed, or false.
